{index}[test results]
The L4YAML CI pipeline runs every test suite on each push and
pull request.
This chapter describes the test result categories and
links to the most recent CI-generated reports.

Test results are generated by the `test-coverage.yml` GitHub
Actions workflow and published alongside this documentation.

